# Portfolio Restructure — Walkthrough

## What Was Done

Restructured the monolithic `Personal Portfolio Website.html` (1504 lines, ~49KB) into a clean, maintainable folder structure with **14 files** across 3 directories.

### Final Structure

```
portfolio/
├── index.html              ← Clean HTML only (~230 lines)
├── css/
│   ├── variables.css       ← CSS variables, reset, body base
│   ├── animations.css      ← All @keyframes + .reveal
│   ├── layout.css          ← Nav, container, sections, footer
│   ├── hero.css            ← Hero section + CTA button
│   ├── about.css           ← About section grid
│   ├── skills.css          ← Skills cards + 3D effects
│   ├── projects.css        ← Project cards + overlays
│   ├── contact.css         ← Form, inputs, contact cards
│   └── responsive.css      ← Media queries (968px, 640px)
├── js/
│   ├── navigation.js       ← Smooth scroll + active nav
│   ├── form.js             ← Form submit animation
│   ├── animations.js       ← Scroll reveal + cursor trail
│   └── cards.js            ← Skill card mouse tracking
└── assets/                 ← Placeholder for images/fonts
```

